Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.24,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.71,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Send word to the lords of \Nevery domain in Melromarc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:32.92,main,KCom,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:39.85,main,KCom,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That is no ordinary forest fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That woman probably started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying to smoke us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.20,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The fire will spread here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:18.09,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,The checkpoint's been closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:20.51,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,and there's an emergency security \Ndeployment along the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.93,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be impossible to cross \Nover to Siltvelt for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.81,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the Devil of the Shield \Nhas abducted Princess Melty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:30.52,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,and is hiding in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:32.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.86,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Let me get your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:36.07,main,Tra,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.28,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen this man around?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.67,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:57.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably give \Nup on going to Siltvelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:04.47,flashback,Shad,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero, you are requested to meet \Nwith Her Majesty the Queen, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:09.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is doing as that Shadow \Nsaid our only option?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.02,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What's the plan, Naofumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to meet the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.30,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:53.92,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,768)}Everlasting Memory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:01.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of demi-humans \Nin this region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.14,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in... I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.43,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.06,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,A nobleman I know is in \Ncharge of this domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:12.52,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,He may be able to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.52,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A nobleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.77,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,These days, humans treat \Ndemi-humans like slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.15,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,but in the past, some of the \Nnobility tried to mediate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.99,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,peaceful coexistence between the two races.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.95,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of that group \Nwas a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.37,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,He was the lord of the domain of Seyaette.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.45,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But he died in the first Wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.33,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,and the nobles that sided with him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:37.38,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,were all shuffled off to remote \Nregions under Father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's hatred of demi-humans is absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Raphtalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The village I'm from is in \NSeyaette's jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:55.31,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Seyaette was attacked \Nby rioters after the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.06,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:07.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,My village was attacked by a \Nmob of Melromarc's soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The more I hear about these people, \Nthe more they disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.08,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like it was your fault, Melty-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.13,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,As royalty, there must have been \Nsomething we could have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.97,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But we did nothing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:29.30,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-san, tell me everything \Nyou remember about those soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:34.22,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Once this all dies down, I'll make \Nsure they're brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.19,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And? This nobleman you \Nknow lives here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.03,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The question is whether \Nor not we can trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.99,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.83,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long, Reichnott.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:04.25,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Melty-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.30,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:10.76,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I am Van Reichnott, the lord of this domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:14.14,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This feeble guy is the \Nnobleman she mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:18.48,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But his stealthiness is off \Nthe charts. What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.19,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,This is no place for a chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.43,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to join me at my mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.20,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:33.99,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,So you reached my domain \Nafter a long escape, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:34.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:39.92,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,The knights informed me that \Nyou started the wildfires
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.88,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,to cover your tracks, Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's a complete lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The first princess probably made it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.22,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:55.18,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I was patrolling the area out \Nof concern for Melty-sama, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.98,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted from your travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.65,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Please rest up here for \Na while, if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.40,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,May I eat, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't trust this guy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.99,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.96,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured, the food isn't poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.63,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:24.17,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.09,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let us eat too, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.60,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Casting doubts on such gracious hospitality?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.35,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,How rude can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't stay here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.48,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,That soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:51.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The longer we stay, the higher the \Nodds of us being sniffed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.78,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.66,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hoping to rest some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:59.41,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed a little, Princess Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.21,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,You used to force yourself\Nto act more mature,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.84,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems traveling with the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:10.80,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,has helped you grow in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure you mean in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.18,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:17.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a racket while we're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.97,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.94,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This bed feels amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So soft and bouncy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.44,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sleep for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when this \Nplace will get attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I make a point of not sleeping \Nat times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, I'll keep watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.87,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,so you can go ahead and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.30,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you listen to what \NRaphtalia-san says, but not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:58.22,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan, I wanna explore this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.81,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.73,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they have any yummy snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:13.24,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you be a bit nicer to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.62,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:28.61,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've been acting really \Nspoiled since meeting Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.38,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,My speech has become cruder, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:35.22,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.51,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:41.06,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You don't understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:43.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I love the way you are now, Mel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:49.61,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you look so cheerful \Nwhen you're talking to Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.32,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.57,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan, have him dote on you just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.57,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.36,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Dote on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.28,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:03.04,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,That's n-not what I'm looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.46,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't found her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:13.96,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Know that I'll have your heads \Nif anything happens to Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:14.92,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.09,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Please rest assured, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.26,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you that I shall rescue Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.31,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.40,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Not my family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.69,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,How much will you make me suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.78,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.85,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,You're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:43.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll take over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:44.91,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:47.08,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.75,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Naofumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.75,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Should I really keep running like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.34,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,As crown princess, there are so many \Nother things I should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:04.35,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't been able to do any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your life comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can worry about your \Nduties after you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:14.65,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't beat yourself up \Ntoo much. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.74,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:28.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are things \Nthat only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.50,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.42,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:35.92,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.21,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:12.46,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is she having that same nightmare again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Rifana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:30.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We've got bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.76,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the lord being taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:39.19,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero! You must get out of here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.57,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:45.49,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,A nobleman from the next town over marched \Nin here and accused us of hiding you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.12,main,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,Find the Devil of the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.49,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Use the kitchen door and \Nescape out the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Filo and Melty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:53.58,main,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.12,main,SolB,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.42,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.75,main,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.46,main,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.09,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Getting ready for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.84,main,SolB,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.80,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.86,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I am Melty Melromarc, \NSecond Princess of Melromarc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.40,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I demand that you cease \Nthis behavior at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.02,main,SolA,0000,0000,0000,,The second princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.02,main,SolB,0000,0000,0000,,The real deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.99,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,My, if it isn't Princess Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.62,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.42,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.88,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I rushed here worried for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.88,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Idol Rabier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:48.51,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that you fought \Nwith Father in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.60,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You heard right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.22,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Are these your troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.52,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,They are indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:56.52,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Have them withdraw from \Nthis mansion immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:00.86,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, where is the \NDevil of the Shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.07,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.32,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:10.57,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to leave me and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:15.33,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to speak with Father directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.79,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,And I shall clear the \NShield Hero's good name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:25.13,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,You will take me to the \Ncapital as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.38,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:31.76,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make arrangements for \Nyour journey at my mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.64,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:43.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to ruin what \NMelty's trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.04,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.71,main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to hell with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here now! This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.56,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for not showing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What were you even doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.35,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.89,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan wanted to play hide and seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.90,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,She said I should hide somewhere \NI wouldn't be found
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.91,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,and not come out, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.33,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,But she never came for me in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:36.87,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.66,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.17,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save Mel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.84,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't hurry up, she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:50.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Abandoning her and running \Naway is an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But she believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:06.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't want to betray someone \Nwho placed their trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I did make her a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You know that Idol guy, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.10,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay behind if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:43.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No. I have my sword now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I want to confront my past!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.28,main,Demi,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.45,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:57.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Demi-humans who love their lord \Nmust've come here for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.41,main,Demi,0000,0000,0000,,Give back Van-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:02.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is convenient. We'll sneak into the \Nmansion while they distract the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.16,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.46,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.93,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, those damned demis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.59,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:22.22,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Just some flies buzzing around. It's \Nnothing you need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.44,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get rid of them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:29.82,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Now, will you tell me where \Nthe Devil of the Shield is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.90,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,As I've told you several \Ntimes, I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.53,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Reichnott?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.21,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the Devil of the Shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.13,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I know no such person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:52.21,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,The only one I know is \Ncalled the Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:57.55,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,As you see, we're having a hard time \Ngetting him to spill the beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:02.72,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I would very much like to avoid \Ngetting rough with you if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.10,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,But as a servant of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:10.73,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I must punish anyone who \Nsides with the Devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.23,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,That is my sacred duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.32,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Go wild, Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:24.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go rescue Melty in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.20,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.63,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.23,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Rescuing Melty takes priority for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We can come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.71,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.84,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:18.09,sign_27732_280_Chimera_Viper_Sh,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chimera Viper Shield Exclusive Skill — Venomous Fang (Med)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's a highly potent venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.39,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't use an antidote quickly,\Nyou'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm willing to save your \Nlife if you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Melty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.40,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:41.61,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I love that valiant look in your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.16,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see it become despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.58,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,and your face warp in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.66,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a good look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.17,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.67,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Idol-sama! It seems the Devil of the Shield\N has infiltrated the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.93,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.68,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:08.93,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.64,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:13.44,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:17.82,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Take one step forward, and the \Nprincess's head will fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So we just have to stand still, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.50,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.51,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:47.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Because I've never heard of a hero \Nwho abandons a child to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.81,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've wasted all my efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.27,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.23,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.90,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You dare make a mockery of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.11,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Torture isn't enough for the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.74,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay with your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.21,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.30,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Lowly demi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.67,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.70,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.94,main,Idol,0000,0000,0000,,S-Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:55.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So many demi-humans begged for \Ntheir lives just like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:58.29,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but you...
